Unusual? Yes, but PUH’s evolutionary logic (rebounds birthing multi-knot systems) allows it—gas giants accrete knots during formation, orbiting pairs stabilize via E8 symmetries. Accounts for massive field (~20 G at poles, 10x Earth’s) from amplified induction (∇θ_k twists ~1.9 log spacings).
